rules: Rule1: If delivery_van has driver Bob, then order_123 becomes delivery_complete
Rule2: Provided that delivery_van has order_123, if delivery_van does not have driver Bob, then delivery_van has driver Alice
Rule3: Whenever order_123 is ready for pickup, delivery_van has order_123
Rule4: Under the condition that order_456 is ready for pickup, delivery_van has order_123
Rule5: If it is not the case that either order_123 is ready for pickup or order_456 is ready for pickup, then delivery_van is vehicle_broken
Rule6: If delivery_van does not have driver Bob, then delivery_van does not have driver Alice
Rule7: Under the condition that delivery_van does not have order_123, delivery_van has order_456
Rule8: Whenever delivery_van does not have order_123, delivery_van does not have order_456
facts: Fact1: It is not the case that delivery_van is vehicle_broken
